&lt;h2&gt;Why you should use PC-Sleep?&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Even though your computer is still working, you might not want, or need, to be there while it finishes up the job at hand. PC Sleep is a simple tool that lets you shut down your computer at a specific time or within a specific time frame, so you can set it and walk away.&lt;/p&gt;

